reviewText: Very poor. Nothing about product work. Google "entrepreneurship" and make a powerpoint with what you found - you have now recreated this course. Don't waste your time or money on the "textbook" either.
Waste of time. V​ery basic course. no depth at all in any topic. the professor barely reads headlines. There are no examples whatsoever. I guarantee you much better content for free on Youtube.

Useful course to get insights into businesses and startups. However, the course has multiple technical issues: referencing content that doesn't exist, databases that learners are supposed to have access to but do not, audio issues, and references a text book that you have to buy.
Felt like it was a way to sell a book rather than teach me anything new
Needs a much more diverse range of success stories
Please fix your audio channels...
EYE OPENING
For online, in this format, not bad.  Good use of real world examples.
Excellent course and a very good accompanying text book

Coming from a recently failed business, I now clearly understand how I made a lot of ignorant errors right from the foundational stag,e even though I did a few things right ( just by trusting my guts & my little knowledge). This course has provided me with an important asset to possess - KNOWLEDGE.

This course helped me a lot to understand my potential for entrepreneurship. Highly educational and very focused as I'm experiencing the topic, of product design. Thank you for the opportunity to learn this.

C​ourse was very informative. The content was provided in a fashion which will allow me to reference key points again whenever situation demands. The Case stoudy based approach taken gave a realistic outlook on the topics covered. Thank you Dr. Green for this amazing learning resource

reviewText: Wonderful.

Una excelente introducción al mundo del emprendimiento y el análisis del mercado antes de crear un nuevo producto o servicio, con análisis mediante ejemplos que hacen de manera más fácil la comprensión de las diferentes etapas del proceso.
Learn about Leadership and Management as a Product Leader
Really enjoyed this course especially the crisp and clear advice on entreperneurs which is very much relevant for organisation employees who are essentially intrapreneurs too.
Highly Educational. Thank you for the wonderful opportunity to learn in a different field career wise. My knowledge on Product Ideation has been broadened.
very​ helpful and specific course for elementary product developers. Thank you Dr. James.

¡Excelente curso! los casos de estudio, las lecturas, los ejemplos y las ideas que son proporcionadas te muestran un panorama claro de cómo desarrollar un proyecto de emprendimiento, esto, combinado con el conocimiento  y la experiencia del Instructor, lo hacen un gran curso.
